{"id":357941,"url":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jeff_Garlin","text":"Jeffrey \"Jeff\" Garlin (born June 5, 1962) is an American stand-up comedian, actor, producer, voice artist, director, writer and author. He is best known for playing Jeff Greene on the HBO show \"Curb Your Enthusiasm\". He is also a producer on the show.\nGarlin was born in Chicago, Illinois. He grew up in Morton Grove, Illinois. Garlin is Jewish.","categories":[],"infobox_types":["comedian"],"annotations":[{"uri":"Americans","surface_form":"American","offset":48},{"uri":"Stand-up_comedian","surface_form":"stand-up comedian","offset":57},{"uri":"Actor","surface_form":"actor","offset":76},{"uri":"Voice_artist","surface_form":"voice artist","offset":93},{"uri":"Writer","surface_form":"writer","offset":117},{"uri":"Author","surface_form":"author","offset":128},{"uri":"Home_Box_Office","surface_form":"HBO","offset":184},{"uri":"Curb_Your_Enthusiasm","surface_form":"Curb Your Enthusiasm","offset":194},{"uri":"Television_producer","surface_form":"producer","offset":230},{"uri":"Chicago%2C_Illinois","surface_form":"Chicago, Illinois","offset":271},{"uri":"Morton_Grove%2C_Illinois","surface_form":"Morton Grove, Illinois","offset":304},{"uri":"Jew","surface_form":"Jew","offset":338}]}